'From Squeak2.8alpha of 12 January 2000 [latest update: #2210] on 2 June 2000 at 9:40:50 am'!"Change Set:		FirstAndLastNDate:			2 June 2000Author:			Dan IngallsExtends the first/last/allButFirst/allButLast protocol to N items.Suggested by David N. Smith."!!SequenceableCollection methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'di 6/2/2000 09:18'!allButFirst	"Answer all but the first element of the receiver."	^ self copyFrom: 2 to: self size! !!SequenceableCollection methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'di 6/2/2000 09:19'!allButFirst: nElements	"Answer all but the first N elements of the receiver."	^ self copyFrom: nElements + 1 to: self size! !!SequenceableCollection methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'di 6/2/2000 09:20'!allButLast	"Answer all but the last element of the receiver."	^ self copyFrom: 1 to: self size - 1! !!SequenceableCollection methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'di 6/2/2000 09:20'!allButLast: nElements	"Answer all but the last N elements of the receiver."	^ self copyFrom: 1 to: self size - nElements! !!SequenceableCollection methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'di 6/2/2000 09:16'!first	"Answer the first element of the receiver.	Raise an error if the collection is empty."	self size = 0 ifTrue: [self errorEmptyCollection].	^ self at: 1! !!SequenceableCollection methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'di 6/2/2000 09:21'!first: nElements	"Answer the first N elements of the receiver."	^ self copyFrom: 1 to: nElements! !!SequenceableCollection methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'di 6/2/2000 09:15'!last	"Answer the last element of the receiver.	Raise an error if the collection is empty."	| size |	(size _ self size) = 0 ifTrue: [self errorEmptyCollection].	^ self at: size! !!SequenceableCollection methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'di 6/2/2000 09:23'!last: nElements	"Answer the last N elements of the receiver."	^ self copyFrom: self size - nElements + 1 to: self size! !OrderedCollection removeSelector: #first!OrderedCollection removeSelector: #last!